   <text><body><seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex45042024-08-2914-22-30" status="finalized"><rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5554">lha</rs> <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5549">shag</rs> dang | <rs type="work" ref="db:5588" ana="corpusmd:named_reference">rgyan</rs> gyi dgongs pa <rs type="work" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5564"><abbr>rigs</abbr> gter</rs> las | <quote source="db:5564" n="VIII.40b"><l><abbr>mi slu</abbr> ma shes don gsal 2 ||</l> <l>rnam grangs pa'ang phye ste smra ||</l></quote> <!--RT VIII.40b, gzhan gyis brtag pa dgag na-->
               <abbr>zhes gsung</abbr> shing | de dgag pa yang | <quote source="db:5564" n="VIII.41ab"><l><abbr>mtshan nyid</abbr> 2 kyis 'jog na ni ||</l> <l>mtshon byed de yang 2 su 'gyur ||</l></quote> <!--VIII.41ab, agaisnt Lha dbang blo-->
               <quote source="db:5564" n="VIII.41cd"><l>mtshon bya <abbr>gnyis su</abbr> 'dod na yang ||</l><l>spyi mtshan 1 pa mi srid 'gyur ||</l></quote> <!--RT VIII.41cd, against rGyan mdzad pa-->
            <quote source="db:5564" n="VIII.42ab?"><l>tha snyad pa dang <abbr>don dam</abbr> pa ||</l> <l>2 ga la yang 2 po 'jug ||</l></quote> <note type="editorial">Different from VIII 42ab against Chos mchog, which reads: ma khyab gcod tshul 'dir mi 'thad || gnyis su 'byed pa dgongs pa min </note> ces dang | 
             <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5552">bram ze</rs>'i bzhed pa la yang | 
            <quote source="db:5564" n="VIII.42cd"><l>mi dgos ma khyab <abbr>mi srid</abbr> 3 ||</l> <l>bden pa'i don <abbr>rtogs</abbr> 'dod na yod ||</l></quote> <!--RT VIII.42cd, against Bram ze-->
            <abbr>ces so</abbr> ||</seg>
            <seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex45042024-08-2914-22-3010" status="finalized"><abbr>mi slu</abbr> ba'i <abbr>don ni</abbr> | <rs type="work" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5564"><abbr>rigs</abbr> gter</rs> las |  
         <quote source="db:5564" n="RTRG ad VIII.44ab">
            <l xml:space="preserve">gang gis gang la <abbr>ji ltar</abbr> <abbr>mi slu</abbr> </l>
         </quote>
      zhes pa 3 bshad cing | don bsdu na | don <abbr>ji ltar</abbr> gnas pa ltar yod pa la <abbr>yod par</abbr> shes med pa la <abbr>med par</abbr> shes pa'o ||</seg><seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex45042024-08-2914-13-45" status="finalized">gzhan yang de ltar 'dod pa de dpyod pa pa'i phyogs su brlan par <abbr>rigs</abbr> pas sun phyin gyi <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:3831">mkhas pa chen po cha pa</rs> swo <note type="editorial">for "la sogs pa"</note> kyis kyang dpyod pa ba'i phyogs su <lb n="6a2"/> <abbr>bslan nas</abbr> dgag pa mdzad pa <abbr>yin no</abbr> ||</seg><seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex45042024-08-2914-18-35" status="finalized"><rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:3892">gangs can mkhas <abbr>pa'i</abbr> gtsug rgyan <abbr>chos rjes</abbr> paNDi ta chen po</rs>s kyang snang yul dang <abbr>gzung yul</abbr> 1 du mdzad nas dgag pa mdzad <abbr>pa'i</abbr> <abbr>rgyu mtshan</abbr> yang <abbr>de 'di</abbr> <lb n="15b8"/> <abbr>yin no</abbr> |</seg><seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex45042024-08-2914-22-283" status="finalized">de ltar <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:3892">chos rje <abbr>thams cad</abbr> mkhyen pa</rs>'i zhal <lb n="63b8"/> mnga' nas kyang | de ltar grub mtha' 4 las <abbr>slob dpon ni</abbr> <abbr>phyi rol</abbr> gyi don <abbr>khas len</abbr> <abbr>pa'i</abbr> tshe <abbr>mdo sde</abbr> pa ltar mdzad la | <abbr>shes bya</abbr> nang la 'jug pa na <abbr>rnam med</abbr> zhal gyis <abbr>bzhes so</abbr> | <abbr>zhes gsungs so</abbr> | ci ste 'dir yang | gang gis <abbr>dngos po</abbr> rnam dpyad na || zhes 1 dang du bral gyi <abbr>gtan tshigs</abbr> <abbr>gsung</abbr> pa <abbr>min nam</abbr> zhe na | <abbr>gsung</abbr> mod kyi | des ni <abbr>dngos po</abbr> mtha' dag <abbr>rang ni</abbr> <abbr>med par</abbr> <pb n="64a"/><lb n="64a1"/> gtan la 'bebs pa ma <abbr>yin no</abbr> || </seg> <seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex45042024-08-2914-22-289" status="finalized">de la snga ma dgag <abbr>pa'i</abbr> phyir | <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:unnamed_reference" ref="db:3892">chos rje</rs> nyid kyi <rs type="work" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5564">rigs pa'i gter</rs> las |
               <quote source="db:5564"><l>la la brda dang tha snyad kyi |</l> 
               <l><abbr>grags</abbr> pa 2 su 'byed pa yod ||</l> 
               <l>tha snyad 'di yi skabs don min ||</l> 
               <l><abbr>mtshan nyid</abbr> de 'dra sngar bkag zin ||</l>
               <l>dngos dang zhen <abbr>pa'i</abbr> <choice><orig>rjod</orig><reg>brjod</reg></choice> rung gis ||</l> 
               <l>brda'i <abbr>grags</abbr> pa'ang 2 zhes zer || </l></quote></seg></body></text></TEI>
